{"schema_version":1,"id":"evt_1780850567156_96620","type":"claim_created","space_id":"slack:T0B8VMZS49J:C0B8TG78JNA","seminar_id":"S1","visibility":"seminar","created_at":"2026-06-07T16:42:47.156557+00:00","actor":{},"payload":{"claim_id":"C1","seminar_id":"S1","paper_id":"self-Users-jiaxinli-Library-Application-Support-CoEducation-seminar-b-08f16c3bb6","by":"self","title":"Slack 入口只是管道","statement":"SeminarBot 的核心分工是 app.py 负责 Slack 事件、消息发送和调度管道，真正的判断交给 brain.py，持久事实交给 canon.py。","type":"concept","source":"self"}}
{"schema_version":1,"id":"evt_1780850567194_96620","type":"claim_created","space_id":"slack:T0B8VMZS49J:C0B8TG78JNA","seminar_id":"S1","visibility":"seminar","created_at":"2026-06-07T16:42:47.194429+00:00","actor":{},"payload":{"claim_id":"C2","seminar_id":"S1","paper_id":"self-Users-jiaxinli-Library-Application-Support-CoEducation-seminar-b-08f16c3bb6","by":"self","title":"本机 Codex 是中央大脑","statement":"SeminarBot 当前通过 brain.py shell 出本机的 `codex exec` 来执行拆主张、分诊、digest 等判断任务，而不是在 Slack 进程内直接实现推理。","type":"core","source":"self"}}
{"schema_version":1,"id":"evt_1780850567231_96620","type":"claim_created","space_id":"slack:T0B8VMZS49J:C0B8TG78JNA","seminar_id":"S1","visibility":"seminar","created_at":"2026-06-07T16:42:47.231610+00:00","actor":{},"payload":{"claim_id":"C3","seminar_id":"S1","paper_id":"self-Users-jiaxinli-Library-Application-Support-CoEducation-seminar-b-08f16c3bb6","by":"self","title":"Git canon 是事实源","statement":"研讨中的 claim、质疑、贡献、来源和 provenance 被沉淀到 `canon/` Git 仓库中，canon 的提交历史构成可追踪的公共共识记录。","type":"core","source":"self"}}
{"schema_version":1,"id":"evt_1780850567268_96620","type":"claim_created","space_id":"slack:T0B8VMZS49J:C0B8TG78JNA","seminar_id":"S1","visibility":"seminar","created_at":"2026-06-07T16:42:47.269024+00:00","actor":{},"payload":{"claim_id":"C4","seminar_id":"S1","paper_id":"self-Users-jiaxinli-Library-Application-Support-CoEducation-seminar-b-08f16c3bb6","by":"self","title":"Source 会先被打包再拆解","statement":"无论 source 来自论文、本地文件夹、GitHub repo、知识库召回还是 SeminarBot 自身源码，系统都会先把它打包成文本 source，再由大脑拆成 claims/concepts。","type":"method","source":"self"}}
{"schema_version":1,"id":"evt_1780850567305_96620","type":"claim_created","space_id":"slack:T0B8VMZS49J:C0B8TG78JNA","seminar_id":"S1","visibility":"seminar","created_at":"2026-06-07T16:42:47.306025+00:00","actor":{},"payload":{"claim_id":"C5","seminar_id":"S1","paper_id":"self-Users-jiaxinli-Library-Application-Support-CoEducation-seminar-b-08f16c3bb6","by":"self","title":"本地导入有权限和路径边界","statement":"本地 file/folder/repo source 默认关闭，只有 `SEMINAR_IMPORT_USER_IDS` 授权用户能从 `PAPER_IMPORT_DIR` 内导入，并且隐藏文件、敏感文件名和非允许后缀会被拒绝。","type":"method","source":"self"}}
{"schema_version":1,"id":"evt_1780850567343_96620","type":"claim_created","space_id":"slack:T0B8VMZS49J:C0B8TG78JNA","seminar_id":"S1","visibility":"seminar","created_at":"2026-06-07T16:42:47.343525+00:00","actor":{},"payload":{"claim_id":"C6","seminar_id":"S1","paper_id":"self-Users-jiaxinli-Library-Application-Support-CoEducation-seminar-b-08f16c3bb6","by":"self","title":"贡献必须被分诊后入库","statement":"成员在 Slack 中对 bot 的质疑或贡献不会直接变成 canon，而是先由大脑判断是否具体、是否承重、对应哪条 claim、属于什么类型，再决定写入或退回追问。","type":"core","source":"self"}}
{"schema_version":1,"id":"evt_1780850567379_96620","type":"claim_created","space_id":"slack:T0B8VMZS49J:C0B8TG78JNA","seminar_id":"S1","visibility":"seminar","created_at":"2026-06-07T16:42:47.379517+00:00","actor":{},"payload":{"claim_id":"C7","seminar_id":"S1","paper_id":"self-Users-jiaxinli-Library-Application-Support-CoEducation-seminar-b-08f16c3bb6","by":"self","title":"自动推进受理解 gate 控制","statement":"SeminarBot 在展示下一条 claim 前会检查成员对已展示 claim/concept 的理解进度，默认至少需要两位成员表达理解，阈值可由 `SEMINAR_ADVANCE_MIN_UNDERSTOOD` 调整。","type":"method","source":"self"}}
{"schema_version":1,"id":"evt_1780850567415_96620","type":"claim_created","space_id":"slack:T0B8VMZS49J:C0B8TG78JNA","seminar_id":"S1","visibility":"seminar","created_at":"2026-06-07T16:42:47.415245+00:00","actor":{},"payload":{"claim_id":"C8","seminar_id":"S1","paper_id":"self-Users-jiaxinli-Library-Application-Support-CoEducation-seminar-b-08f16c3bb6","by":"self","title":"Private copilot 可填理解表","statement":"如果配置 private copilot 映射，SeminarBot 会通过 Slack marker 或 A2A profile 请求 copilot 回传学生的概念理解状态，并优先用这些状态作为推进 gate 的依据。","type":"method","source":"self"}}
{"schema_version":1,"id":"evt_1780850567451_96620","type":"claim_created","space_id":"slack:T0B8VMZS49J:C0B8TG78JNA","seminar_id":"S1","visibility":"seminar","created_at":"2026-06-07T16:42:47.451589+00:00","actor":{},"payload":{"claim_id":"C9","seminar_id":"S1","paper_id":"self-Users-jiaxinli-Library-Application-Support-CoEducation-seminar-b-08f16c3bb6","by":"self","title":"A2A 只共享学习状态","statement":"SeminarBot 的 A2A-over-Slack profile 规定 bot-to-bot 协调只交换概念清单、学习状态请求和概念进度 artifact，不读取 private copilot 的内部记忆或私人知识库。","type":"concept","source":"self"}}
{"schema_version":1,"id":"evt_1780850567487_96620","type":"claim_created","space_id":"slack:T0B8VMZS49J:C0B8TG78JNA","seminar_id":"S1","visibility":"seminar","created_at":"2026-06-07T16:42:47.487605+00:00","actor":{},"payload":{"claim_id":"C10","seminar_id":"S1","paper_id":"self-Users-jiaxinli-Library-Application-Support-CoEducation-seminar-b-08f16c3bb6","by":"self","title":"证据链接不暴露 PDF 路径","statement":"`/seminar evidence-link` 和 evidence viewer 会为 claim 生成随机 token 的 PDF 原文页链接，token 元数据存在 canon 中，URL 不直接暴露本地 PDF 路径。","type":"method","source":"self"}}
{"schema_version":1,"id":"evt_1780850567522_96620","type":"claim_created","space_id":"slack:T0B8VMZS49J:C0B8TG78JNA","seminar_id":"S1","visibility":"seminar","created_at":"2026-06-07T16:42:47.522648+00:00","actor":{},"payload":{"claim_id":"C11","seminar_id":"S1","paper_id":"self-Users-jiaxinli-Library-Application-Support-CoEducation-seminar-b-08f16c3bb6","by":"self","title":"记忆空间按 Slack channel 隔离","statement":"SeminarBot 按 Slack team/channel 维护独立 memory space；不同 channel 可以并行主持，同一 channel 不并发但可连续进行多场 seminar 并共享长期记忆。","type":"core","source":"self"}}
{"schema_version":1,"id":"evt_1780850567557_96620","type":"claim_created","space_id":"slack:T0B8VMZS49J:C0B8TG78JNA","seminar_id":"S1","visibility":"seminar","created_at":"2026-06-07T16:42:47.557970+00:00","actor":{},"payload":{"claim_id":"C12","seminar_id":"S1","paper_id":"self-Users-jiaxinli-Library-Application-Support-CoEducation-seminar-b-08f16c3bb6","by":"self","title":"Cognee 是派生召回层","statement":"Git canon 仍是事实源，Cognee 只作为可重建的 graph/vector recall 层，用于补充联想召回；其失败或超时不应阻断主持流程。","type":"concept","source":"self"}}
{"schema_version":1,"id":"evt_1780850567594_96620","type":"claim_created","space_id":"slack:T0B8VMZS49J:C0B8TG78JNA","seminar_id":"S1","visibility":"seminar","created_at":"2026-06-07T16:42:47.594665+00:00","actor":{},"payload":{"claim_id":"C13","seminar_id":"S1","paper_id":"self-Users-jiaxinli-Library-Application-Support-CoEducation-seminar-b-08f16c3bb6","by":"self","title":"运行态与发布态分离","statement":"launchd 部署会把代码和 `.env` 同步到 Application Support 的 runtime copy，并保留运行态 `canon/` 和 Cognee 状态；代码或环境变更后需要重新 install 才会进入后台 job。","type":"method","source":"self"}}
{"schema_version":1,"id":"evt_1780850567630_96620","type":"claim_created","space_id":"slack:T0B8VMZS49J:C0B8TG78JNA","seminar_id":"S1","visibility":"seminar","created_at":"2026-06-07T16:42:47.630558+00:00","actor":{},"payload":{"claim_id":"C14","seminar_id":"S1","paper_id":"self-Users-jiaxinli-Library-Application-Support-CoEducation-seminar-b-08f16c3bb6","by":"self","title":"个人订阅原型不能共享服务化","statement":"README 明确把本机 `codex exec` 用法限定为个人、单账户、本机原型，不应部署成多人共享账户服务；正式服务化应把 brain.py 的 `_run` 换成 API key 调用。","type":"core","source":"self"}}
